\(2\)]\)\[GothicCapitalD](r)\!\(\*SuperscriptBox[\(p\), \(2\)]\), we can roll \
up \[CapitalKappa] into the radius p:\>\"", "]"}], ";"}], "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"Print", "[", 
     RowBox[{"\"\<     \[GothicCapitalD](r) = \>\"", ",", 
      RowBox[{"\[GothicCapitalD]", "[", "r", "]"}], ",", "\"\<.\>\""}], "]"}],
     ";"}], "\[IndentingNewLine]", "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"Print", "[", "]"}], ";"}], "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
    "Print", "[", "\"\<Plugging back in, \!\(\*SubscriptBox[\(R\), \(00\)]\) \
