see that \!\(\*SubscriptBox[\(R\), \(44\)]\) has also become satisfied:\>\"", 
     "]"}], ";"}], "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"For", "[", 
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{"\[Mu]", "=", "1"}], ",", 
      RowBox[{"\[Mu]", "\[LessEqual]", "4"}], ",", 
      RowBox[{"\[Mu]", "++"}], ",", 
      RowBox[{"If", "[", 
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{"!", 
         RowBox[{"\[Mu]", "==", "3"}]}], ",", "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
