   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
    "Print", "[", "\"\<The solution below involves setting \
\[GothicCapitalD](r)=\!\(\*FractionBox[\(\[Beta]\), \
\(2\)]\)\!\(\*SuperscriptBox[\(r\), \(2\)]\), an educated guess. This is not \
