\[Omega])\!\(\*SuperscriptBox[\(]\), \(2\)]\) = \
a[t\!\(\*SuperscriptBox[\(]\), \
\(2\)]\)\[InvisibleSpace]Cosh[i\!\(\*SqrtBox[\(2  \[Alpha]\\\ \[Beta]\\\ \
\[CapitalLambda]\)]\)(r-\[Omega])\!\(\*SuperscriptBox[\(]\), \(2\)]\)\>\"", 
     "]"}], ";"}], "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
   RowBox[{
