    "Print", "[", "\"\<    Commonly in Case d_II we would have \[Alpha] = -\
\[Beta] = \!\(\*FractionBox[\(1\), \(2\)]\) so that\>\"", "]"}], ";"}], "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
   RowBox[{
