\[GothicCapitalC]^(-1) $CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD]^(-1) $CellContext`\
\[CapitalBeta]^(-1) Derivative[1][$CellContext`\[GothicCapitalC]] 
    Derivative[1][$CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD]], 
   " = ", (-2) $CellContext`\[CapitalLambda]],
  Editable->False]], "Print",
