   Derivative[1][$CellContext`\[GothicCapitalC]] 
   Derivative[1][$CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD]] + 
   Rational[-1, 
      2] $CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD]^(-2) $CellContext`\[CapitalBeta]^(-1) 
    Derivative[1][$CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD]]^2, " = ", 
   3 $CellContext`\[CapitalLambda]],
  Editable->False]], "Print",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.980535114582703*^9},
 CellLabel->
  "During evaluation of \
In[16561]:=",ExpressionUUID->"a3b59f17-e945-4e71-b4ee-dbacfb071805"],

Cell[BoxData["\<\"\"\>"], "Print",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.9805351145834007`*^9},
 CellLabel->
  "During evaluation of \
In[16561]:=",ExpressionUUID->"091d2928-7a6b-4b09-9f5a-38afa9dba400"],

Cell[BoxData["\<\"Unfortunately, the formula for \[CapitalBeta](r) is lengthy \
and makes the equations much worse when plugging back in, so we try a \
different approach.\"\>"], "Print",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.9805351145838747`*^9},
 CellLabel->
  "During evaluation of \
In[16561]:=",ExpressionUUID->"e94ed18d-691e-41b8-b7c2-c95b781f9073"],

Cell[BoxData["\<\"\"\>"], "Print",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.980535115095429*^9},
 CellLabel->
  "During evaluation of \
In[16561]:=",ExpressionUUID->"307499a1-cf13-4ffb-8caf-3938025c618e"],

Cell[BoxData["\<\"Instead of solving 2\\!\\(\\*SubscriptBox[\\(R\\), \
\\(00\\)]\\)-\\!\\(\\*SubscriptBox[\\(R\\), \
\\(11\\)]\\)+2\\!\\(\\*SubscriptBox[\\(R\\), \\(22\\)]\\), we can solve \
\\!\\(\\*SubscriptBox[\\(R\\), \\(00\\)]\\) for \[ScriptCapitalA] or \
\[CapitalBeta] (but not \[GothicCapitalD]). Solving for \[CapitalBeta] \
results in unsolvable equations. However, solving for \[ScriptCapitalA] is \
more productive:\"\>"], "Print",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.980535115096409*^9},
 CellLabel->
  "During evaluation of \
In[16561]:=",ExpressionUUID->"88e5dce5-fe4a-4ca4-b84c-35326f0fb447"],

Cell[BoxData[
 InterpretationBox[
  RowBox[{"\<\"     \[ScriptCapitalA](t) = \"\>", "\[InvisibleSpace]", 
   FractionBox[
    RowBox[{"4", " ", 
     SuperscriptBox["c", "2"], " ", "r", " ", "\[GothicCapitalC]", " ", 
     SuperscriptBox["\[CapitalBeta]", "2"], " ", 
     SuperscriptBox[
      OverscriptBox["a", "."], "2"]}], 
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"4", " ", 
      SuperscriptBox["c", "2"], " ", "r", " ", "\[GothicCapitalC]", " ", 
      SuperscriptBox["\[CapitalBeta]", "2"], " ", "\[Gamma]"}], "+", 
     RowBox[{"4", " ", 
      SuperscriptBox["a", "2"], " ", "r", " ", "\[GothicCapitalC]", " ", 
      "\[GothicCapitalD]", " ", 
      SuperscriptBox["\[CapitalBeta]", "2"], " ", "\[CapitalLambda]"}], "+", 
     RowBox[{"4", " ", 
      SuperscriptBox["a", "2"], " ", "\[GothicCapitalC]", " ", 
      "\[CapitalBeta]", " ", 
      SuperscriptBox["\[GothicCapitalD]", "\[Prime]",
       MultilineFunction->None]}], "+", 
     RowBox[{"2", " ", 
      SuperscriptBox["a", "2"], " ", "r", " ", "\[CapitalBeta]", " ", 
      SuperscriptBox["\[GothicCapitalC]", "\[Prime]",
       MultilineFunction->None], " ", 
      SuperscriptBox["\[GothicCapitalD]", "\[Prime]",
       MultilineFunction->None]}], "-", 
     RowBox[{
      SuperscriptBox["a", "2"], " ", "r", " ", "\[GothicCapitalC]", " ", 
      SuperscriptBox["\[GothicCapitalD]", "\[Prime]",
       MultilineFunction->None], " ", 
      SuperscriptBox["\[CapitalBeta]", "\[Prime]",
       MultilineFunction->None]}], "+", 
     RowBox[{"2", " ", 
      SuperscriptBox["a", "2"], " ", "r", " ", "\[GothicCapitalC]", " ", 
      "\[CapitalBeta]", " ", 
      SuperscriptBox["\[GothicCapitalD]", "\[Prime]\[Prime]",
       MultilineFunction->None]}]}]]}],
  SequenceForm[
  "     \[ScriptCapitalA](t) = ", 
   4 $CellContext`c^2 $CellContext`r $CellContext`\[GothicCapitalC] \
$CellContext`\[CapitalBeta]^2 OverDot[$CellContext`a, 1]^2/(
   4 $CellContext`c^2 $CellContext`r $CellContext`\[GothicCapitalC] \
$CellContext`\[CapitalBeta]^2 $CellContext`\[Gamma] + 
   4 $CellContext`a^2 $CellContext`r $CellContext`\[GothicCapitalC] \
$CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD] $CellContext`\[CapitalBeta]^2 $CellContext`\
\[CapitalLambda] + 
   4 $CellContext`a^2 $CellContext`\[GothicCapitalC] $CellContext`\
\[CapitalBeta] Derivative[1][$CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD]] + 
   2 $CellContext`a^2 $CellContext`r $CellContext`\[CapitalBeta] 
    Derivative[1][$CellContext`\[GothicCapitalC]] 
    Derivative[
     1][$CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD]] - $CellContext`a^2 $CellContext`r \
$CellContext`\[GothicCapitalC] Derivative[1][$CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD]] 
   Derivative[1][$CellContext`\[CapitalBeta]] + 
   2 $CellContext`a^2 $CellContext`r $CellContext`\[GothicCapitalC] \
$CellContext`\[CapitalBeta] Derivative[2][$CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD]])],
  Editable->False]], "Print",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.9805351150974493`*^9},
 CellLabel->
  "During evaluation of \
In[16561]:=",ExpressionUUID->"572a95d8-023f-4db9-a675-2a98524f5caa"],

Cell[BoxData["\<\"            where \[Gamma] is a constant of \
integration\"\>"], "Print",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.980535115098167*^9},
 CellLabel->
  "During evaluation of \
In[16561]:=",ExpressionUUID->"1df2f841-a72f-4ea5-b705-8e7c6ba43af3"],

Cell[BoxData["\<\"\"\>"], "Print",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.980535115155573*^9},
 CellLabel->
  "During evaluation of \
In[16561]:=",ExpressionUUID->"40a8a966-99b8-4583-9a7c-f9cea1fb46fd"],

Cell[BoxData["\<\"Observe that the numerator divided by r \[GothicCapitalC] \
\\!\\(\\*SuperscriptBox[\\(\[CapitalBeta]\\), \\(2\\)]\\) is strictly a \
function of t. In order for the whole expression to be strictly a function of \
t, the denominator divided by r \[GothicCapitalC] \\!\\(\\*SuperscriptBox[\\(\
\[CapitalBeta]\\), \\(2\\)]\\) must also equal some function of t, say \
\[ScriptF](t).\"\>"], "Print",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.980535115156508*^9},
 CellLabel->
  "During evaluation of \
In[16561]:=",ExpressionUUID->"7b12b458-1ab4-44ca-ad5a-ca78829aaad7"],

Cell[BoxData["\<\"\"\>"], "Print",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.98053511515736*^9},
 CellLabel->
  "During evaluation of \
In[16561]:=",ExpressionUUID->"c95f6afa-65c1-4e1f-aaf3-b3021231f40c"],

Cell[BoxData[
 InterpretationBox[
  RowBox[{"\<\"     \\!\\(\\*FractionBox[\\(Denominator\\), \\(r\\\\ \
\[GothicCapitalC]\\\\ \\*SuperscriptBox[\\(\[CapitalBeta]\\), \\(2\\)]\\)]\\) \
= \[ScriptF](t):  \"\>", "\[InvisibleSpace]", 
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"4", " ", 
     SuperscriptBox["c", "2"], " ", "\[Gamma]"}], "+", 
    RowBox[{"4", " ", 
     SuperscriptBox["a", "2"], " ", "\[GothicCapitalD]", " ", 
     "\[CapitalLambda]"}], "+", 
    FractionBox[
     RowBox[{"4", " ", 
      SuperscriptBox["a", "2"], " ", 
      SuperscriptBox["\[GothicCapitalD]", "\[Prime]",
       MultilineFunction->None]}], 
     RowBox[{"r", " ", "\[CapitalBeta]"}]], "+", 
    FractionBox[
     RowBox[{"2", " ", 
      SuperscriptBox["a", "2"], " ", 
      SuperscriptBox["\[GothicCapitalC]", "\[Prime]",
       MultilineFunction->None], " ", 
      SuperscriptBox["\[GothicCapitalD]", "\[Prime]",
       MultilineFunction->None]}], 
     RowBox[{"\[GothicCapitalC]", " ", "\[CapitalBeta]"}]], "-", 
    FractionBox[
     RowBox[{
      SuperscriptBox["a", "2"], " ", 
      SuperscriptBox["\[GothicCapitalD]", "\[Prime]",
       MultilineFunction->None], " ", 
      SuperscriptBox["\[CapitalBeta]", "\[Prime]",
       MultilineFunction->None]}], 
     SuperscriptBox["\[CapitalBeta]", "2"]], "+", 
    FractionBox[
     RowBox[{"2", " ", 
      SuperscriptBox["a", "2"], " ", 
      SuperscriptBox["\[GothicCapitalD]", "\[Prime]\[Prime]",
       MultilineFunction->None]}], "\[CapitalBeta]"]}], 
   "\[InvisibleSpace]", "\<\" = \"\>", "\[InvisibleSpace]", 
   RowBox[{"\[ScriptF]", "[", "t", "]"}]}],
  SequenceForm[
  "     \!\(\*FractionBox[\(Denominator\), \(r\\ \[GothicCapitalC]\\ \
\*SuperscriptBox[\(\[CapitalBeta]\), \(2\)]\)]\) = \[ScriptF](t):  ", 
   4 $CellContext`c^2 $CellContext`\[Gamma] + 
   4 $CellContext`a^2 $CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD] $CellContext`\
\[CapitalLambda] + 
   4 $CellContext`a^2 $CellContext`r^(-1) $CellContext`\[CapitalBeta]^(-1) 
    Derivative[1][$CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD]] + 
   2 $CellContext`a^2 $CellContext`\[GothicCapitalC]^(-1) $CellContext`\
\[CapitalBeta]^(-1) Derivative[1][$CellContext`\[GothicCapitalC]] 
    Derivative[
     1][$CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD]] - $CellContext`a^2 $CellContext`\
\[CapitalBeta]^(-2) Derivative[1][$CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD]] 
   Derivative[1][$CellContext`\[CapitalBeta]] + 
   2 $CellContext`a^2 $CellContext`\[CapitalBeta]^(-1) 
    Derivative[2][$CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD]], " = ", 
   $CellContext`\[ScriptF][$CellContext`t]],
  Editable->False]], "Print",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.9805351151581*^9},
 CellLabel->
  "During evaluation of \
In[16561]:=",ExpressionUUID->"539c9df7-8e99-4ddd-a879-d23934237381"],

Cell[BoxData["\<\"\"\>"], "Print",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.980535116072901*^9},
 CellLabel->
  "During evaluation of \
In[16561]:=",ExpressionUUID->"b6f5b0b1-3f5c-4636-b086-dc7eead47d87"],

Cell[BoxData["\<\"We can solve this equation for \[CapitalBeta](r):\"\>"], \
"Print",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.980535116073844*^9},
 CellLabel->
  "During evaluation of \
In[16561]:=",ExpressionUUID->"241af958-a805-47e7-a969-67e0047d3c4b"],

Cell[BoxData[
 InterpretationBox[
  RowBox[{"\<\"     \[CapitalBeta][r] = \"\>", "\[InvisibleSpace]", 
   FractionBox[
    RowBox[{
     SuperscriptBox["r", "4"], " ", 
     SuperscriptBox["\[GothicCapitalC]", "2"], " ", 
     SuperscriptBox[
      RowBox[{"(", 
       SuperscriptBox["\[GothicCapitalD]", "\[Prime]",
        MultilineFunction->None], ")"}], "2"]}], 
    RowBox[{"\[Alpha]", "-", 
     TemplateBox[{
       FractionBox[
        RowBox[{
          SuperscriptBox["\[GothicCapitalC]", "2"], " ", 
          RowBox[{"(", 
            RowBox[{
              RowBox[{"-", "\[ScriptF]"}], "+", 
              RowBox[{"4", " ", 
                SuperscriptBox["c", "2"], " ", "\[Gamma]"}], "+", 
              RowBox[{"4", " ", 
                SuperscriptBox["a", "2"], " ", "\[GothicCapitalD]", " ", 
                "\[CapitalLambda]"}]}], ")"}], " ", 
          SuperscriptBox["\[Rho]", "4"], " ", 
          SuperscriptBox[
          "\[GothicCapitalD]", "\[Prime]", MultilineFunction -> None]}], 
        SuperscriptBox["a", "2"]], "\[Rho]", "1", "r"},
      "InactiveIntegrate",
      DisplayFunction->(RowBox[{
         SubsuperscriptBox[
          StyleBox["\[Integral]", "Inactive"], #3, #4], 
         RowBox[{#, 
           RowBox[{
             StyleBox["\[DifferentialD]", "Inactive"], #2}]}]}]& ),
      InterpretationFunction->(RowBox[{
         RowBox[{"Inactive", "[", "Integrate", "]"}], "[", 
         RowBox[{#, ",", 
           RowBox[{"{", 
             RowBox[{#2, ",", #3, ",", #4}], "}"}]}], "]"}]& )]}]], 
   "\[InvisibleSpace]", "\<\"    where \[Alpha] is a constant of integration.\
\"\>"}],
  SequenceForm[
  "     \[CapitalBeta][r] = ", $CellContext`r^4 \
$CellContext`\[GothicCapitalC]^2 
   Derivative[1][$CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD]]^2/($CellContext`\[Alpha] - 
   Inactive[Integrate][$CellContext`a^(-2) $CellContext`\[GothicCapitalC]^2 \
(-$CellContext`\[ScriptF] + 4 $CellContext`c^2 $CellContext`\[Gamma] + 
     4 $CellContext`a^2 $CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD] $CellContext`\
\[CapitalLambda]) $CellContext`\[Rho]^4 
    Derivative[1][$CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD]], {$CellContext`\[Rho], 
     1, $CellContext`r}]), "    where \[Alpha] is a constant of integration."],
  Editable->False]], "Print",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.980535116074622*^9},
 CellLabel->
  "During evaluation of \
In[16561]:=",ExpressionUUID->"9c6ea582-7bdb-4f33-9612-c660bcde253a"],

Cell[BoxData["\<\"\"\>"], "Print",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.980535116077737*^9},
 CellLabel->
  "During evaluation of \
In[16561]:=",ExpressionUUID->"69cb5700-156a-4a34-a012-5020079a7ffb"],

Cell[BoxData["\<\"This formula for \[CapitalBeta](r) makes the equations \
unwieldy when it is plugged back in, so we don't use it. It's existence is \
sufficient to show that the equation\"\>"], "Print",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.980535116078497*^9},
 CellLabel->
  "During evaluation of \
In[16561]:=",ExpressionUUID->"219b7c7f-aecb-4baf-885b-4ab7e01cb8fa"],

Cell[BoxData["\<\"     \\!\\(\\*FractionBox[\\(Denominator\\), \\(r\\\\ \
\[GothicCapitalC]\\\\ \\*SuperscriptBox[\\(\[CapitalBeta]\\), \\(2\\)]\\)]\\) \
= \[ScriptF](t)\"\>"], "Print",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.9805351160791397`*^9},
 CellLabel->
  "During evaluation of \
In[16561]:=",ExpressionUUID->"7cbbef0f-fea8-442c-860e-274fc78a7d57"],

Cell[BoxData["\<\"\"\>"], "Print",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.9805351160798187`*^9},
 CellLabel->
  "During evaluation of \
In[16561]:=",ExpressionUUID->"1e58a91d-c553-4572-8da9-dbf35712154e"],

Cell[BoxData["\<\"is solvable. This means that \[ScriptCapitalA](t) can \
(again) be compactly expressed as\"\>"], "Print",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.980535116080323*^9},
 CellLabel->
  "During evaluation of \
In[16561]:=",ExpressionUUID->"c75a20ab-766b-4ed1-9691-ee31ec3f8ff7"],

Cell[BoxData[
 InterpretationBox[
  RowBox[{"\<\"     \[ScriptCapitalA](t) = \
\\!\\(\\*FractionBox[\\(Numerator\\), \\(Denominator\\)]\\) = \"\>", "\[InvisibleSpace]", 
   FractionBox[
    RowBox[{"4", " ", 
     SuperscriptBox["c", "2"], " ", 
     SuperscriptBox[
      OverscriptBox["a", "."], "2"]}], "\[ScriptF]"], 
   "\[InvisibleSpace]", "\<\".\"\>"}],
  SequenceForm[
  "     \[ScriptCapitalA](t) = \!\(\*FractionBox[\(Numerator\), \(Denominator\
\)]\) = ", 4 $CellContext`c^2 $CellContext`\[ScriptF]^(-1) 
   OverDot[$CellContext`a, 1]^2, "."],
  Editable->False]], "Print",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.980535116080905*^9},
 CellLabel->
  "During evaluation of \
In[16561]:=",ExpressionUUID->"1c4d0891-85b5-4754-ab2c-3758f160c622"],

Cell[BoxData["\<\"\"\>"], "Print",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.980535116081511*^9},
 CellLabel->
  "During evaluation of \
In[16561]:=",ExpressionUUID->"7f71b1fb-b5cc-4ecf-b93f-18eb1b344e8d"],

Cell[BoxData["\<\"Plugging \[ScriptCapitalA] back into the equations should \
make \\!\\(\\*SubscriptBox[\\(R\\), \\(00\\)]\\) into the identity, 0=0, but \
it doesn't because we have suppessed the formula for \[CapitalBeta]:\"\>"], \
"Print",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.980535116082013*^9},
 CellLabel->
  "During evaluation of \
In[16561]:=",ExpressionUUID->"8affcd08-b361-41c9-b974-511aee5056cb"],

Cell[BoxData[
 InterpretationBox[
  RowBox[{"\<\"     \\!\\(\\*SubscriptBox[\\(R\\), \\(00\\)]\\):  \"\>", "\[InvisibleSpace]", 
   RowBox[{
    FractionBox[
     OverscriptBox["\[ScriptF]", "."], 
     RowBox[{"8", " ", "a", " ", "\[GothicCapitalD]", " ", 
      OverscriptBox["a", "."]}]], "-", 
    FractionBox[
     SuperscriptBox["\[GothicCapitalD]", "\[Prime]",
      MultilineFunction->None], 
     RowBox[{"r", " ", "\[GothicCapitalD]", " ", "\[CapitalBeta]"}]], "-", 
    FractionBox[
     RowBox[{
      SuperscriptBox["\[GothicCapitalC]", "\[Prime]",
       MultilineFunction->None], " ", 
      SuperscriptBox["\[GothicCapitalD]", "\[Prime]",
       MultilineFunction->None]}], 
     RowBox[{
     "2", " ", "\[GothicCapitalC]", " ", "\[GothicCapitalD]", " ", 
      "\[CapitalBeta]"}]], "+", 
    FractionBox[
     RowBox[{
      SuperscriptBox["\[GothicCapitalD]", "\[Prime]",
       MultilineFunction->None], " ", 
      SuperscriptBox["\[CapitalBeta]", "\[Prime]",
       MultilineFunction->None]}], 
     RowBox[{"4", " ", "\[GothicCapitalD]", " ", 
      SuperscriptBox["\[CapitalBeta]", "2"]}]], "-", 
    FractionBox[
     SuperscriptBox["\[GothicCapitalD]", "\[Prime]\[Prime]",
      MultilineFunction->None], 
     RowBox[{"2", " ", "\[GothicCapitalD]", " ", "\[CapitalBeta]"}]]}], 
   "\[InvisibleSpace]", "\<\" = \"\>", "\[InvisibleSpace]", 
   "\[CapitalLambda]", "\[InvisibleSpace]", "\<\".\"\>"}],
  SequenceForm[
  "     \!\(\*SubscriptBox[\(R\), \(00\)]\):  ", 
   Rational[1, 8] $CellContext`a^(-1) $CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD]^(-1) 
    OverDot[$CellContext`a, 1]^(-1) 
    OverDot[$CellContext`\[ScriptF], 
      1] - $CellContext`r^(-1) $CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD]^(-1) \
$CellContext`\[CapitalBeta]^(-1) 
   Derivative[1][$CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD]] + 
   Rational[-1, 
      2] $CellContext`\[GothicCapitalC]^(-1) \
$CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD]^(-1) $CellContext`\[CapitalBeta]^(-1) 
    Derivative[1][$CellContext`\[GothicCapitalC]] 
    Derivative[1][$CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD]] + 
   Rational[1, 
      4] $CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD]^(-1) $CellContext`\[CapitalBeta]^(-2) 
    Derivative[1][$CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD]] 
    Derivative[1][$CellContext`\[CapitalBeta]] + 
   Rational[-1, 
      2] $CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD]^(-1) $CellContext`\[CapitalBeta]^(-1) 
    Derivative[2][$CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD]], 
   " = ", $CellContext`\[CapitalLambda], "."],
  Editable->False]], "Print",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.980535116145056*^9},
 CellLabel->
  "During evaluation of \
In[16561]:=",ExpressionUUID->"4ae5bf7f-b859-4df7-ad62-480edbf7e8b8"],

Cell[BoxData["\<\"\"\>"], "Print",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.980535116148262*^9},
 CellLabel->
  "During evaluation of \
In[16561]:=",ExpressionUUID->"ac20aeb8-ac0f-41e9-b3f8-a5357fbed872"],

Cell[BoxData["\<\"We can restore \\!\\(\\*SubscriptBox[\\(R\\), \\(00\\)]\\) \
as an identity if we eliminate t from \\!\\(\\*SubscriptBox[\\(R\\), \
\\(00\\)]\\) and then re-solve for \[CapitalBeta](r). We eliminate t by \
solving \\!\\(\\*OverscriptBox[\\(\[ScriptF]\\), \\(.\\)]\\) = \[Kappa] a \\!\
\\(\\*OverscriptBox[\\(a\\), \\(.\\)]\\), where \[Kappa] is a proportionality \
constant:\"\>"], "Print",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.980535116149066*^9},
 CellLabel->
  "During evaluation of \
In[16561]:=",ExpressionUUID->"c7331b20-6b9e-498b-9df8-f7c2b96b718d"],

Cell[BoxData[
 InterpretationBox[
  RowBox[{"\<\"     \[ScriptF](t) = \"\>", "\[InvisibleSpace]", 
   RowBox[{"\[Zeta]", "+", 
    RowBox[{
     FractionBox["1", "2"], " ", "\[Kappa]", " ", 
     SuperscriptBox[
      RowBox[{"a", "[", "t", "]"}], "2"]}]}], 
   "\[InvisibleSpace]", "\<\"  where \[Zeta] is a constant of \
integration.\"\>"}],
  SequenceForm[
  "     \[ScriptF](t) = ", $CellContext`\[Zeta] + 
   Rational[1, 2] $CellContext`\[Kappa] $CellContext`a[$CellContext`t]^2, 
   "  where \[Zeta] is a constant of integration."],
  Editable->False]], "Print",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.9805351161499434`*^9},
 CellLabel->
  "During evaluation of \
In[16561]:=",ExpressionUUID->"baf7ab2e-fcf6-4bcc-b62c-9b4b5585715b"],

Cell[BoxData["\<\"\"\>"], "Print",
