Cell[BoxData["\<\"When we re-solve \\!\\(\\*SubscriptBox[\\(R\\), \
\\(00\\)]\\) for \[CapitalBeta](r), we obtain the desired simplified \
\[CapitalBeta](r) formula, one that has constant \[Kappa] instead of the \
\[ScriptF](t) function:\"\>"], "Print",
