Cell[BoxData["\<\"However, \\!\\(\\*SubscriptBox[\\(R\\), \\(11\\)]\\) and \
\\!\\(\\*SubscriptBox[\\(R\\), \\(22\\)]\\) have many terms and also include \
the \[CapitalBeta](r) integral. The simplest combination of the equations is \
\\!\\(\\*SubscriptBox[\\(R\\), \\(11\\)]\\)-2\\!\\(\\*SubscriptBox[\\(R\\), \
\\(22\\)]\\) and even it has 6 terms involving the integral plus 8 more \
terms.\"\>"], "Print",
