$CellContext`r^(-6) $CellContext`\[Alpha] 
    Derivative[
      1][$CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD]]^(-2) - $CellContext`r^(-5) \
$CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD]^(-1) $CellContext`\[Alpha]/Derivative[
   1][$CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD]] + 
   Rational[-1, 4] $CellContext`r^(-1) $CellContext`\[Kappa]/Derivative[
    1][$CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD]] + 
   2 $CellContext`r^(-1) $CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD] $CellContext`\
\[CapitalLambda]/Derivative[
    1][$CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD]] + $CellContext`r^(-5) $CellContext`\
\[Alpha] Derivative[1][$CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD]]^(-3) 
