   Derivative[1][$CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD]]^(-2) 
   Inactive[Integrate][
    Rational[-1, 2] ($CellContext`\[Kappa] - 
      8 $CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD] $CellContext`\[CapitalLambda]) \
$CellContext`\[Rho]^4 
     Derivative[1][$CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD]], {$CellContext`\[Rho], 
      1, $CellContext`r}] + $CellContext`r^(-5) \
$CellContext`\[GothicCapitalD]^(-1) 
