Cell[BoxData["\<\"We have found an exact solution to the \[CapitalLambda] \
field equations. The formula for \[GothicCapitalD], above, was based upon the \
denominators being proportional, for which there is no requirement. Thus, \
there could be other, more general solutions.\"\>"], "Print",
