Cell[BoxData["\<\"I found that I could \
\\!\\(\\*StyleBox[\\\"algebraically\\\",FontSlant->\\\"Italic\\\"]\\) solve 4\
\\!\\(\\*SubscriptBox[\\(R\\), \\(00\\)]\\)-\\!\\(\\*SubscriptBox[\\(R\\), \
\\(11\\)]\\) for \[CapitalBeta], \
\\!\\(\\*StyleBox[\\\"algebraically\\\",FontSlant->\\\"Italic\\\"]\\) solve \
