\\(00\\)]\\)-3\\!\\(\\*SubscriptBox[\\(R\\), \\(22\\)]\\), \
\\!\\(\\*SubscriptBox[\\(R\\), \\(00\\)]\\)-3\\!\\(\\*SubscriptBox[\\(R\\), \
\\(44\\)]\\), or 4\\!\\(\\*SubscriptBox[\\(R\\), \
\\(00\\)]\\)-\\!\\(\\*SubscriptBox[\\(R\\), \
\\(11\\)]\\)-12\\!\\(\\*SubscriptBox[\\(R\\), \\(44\\)]\\) for \
\[ScriptCapitalA], Dsolve \\!\\(\\*SubscriptBox[\\(R\\), \\(11\\)]\\) or \
\\!\\(\\*SubscriptBox[\\(R\\), \\(22\\)]\\)-\\!\\(\\*SubscriptBox[\\(R\\), \
\\(44\\)]\\) for \[CapitalBeta], or DSolve 3\\!\\(\\*SubscriptBox[\\(R\\), \
\\(11\\)]\\)+4\\!\\(\\*SubscriptBox[\\(R\\), \
\\(22\\)]\\)-4\\!\\(\\*SubscriptBox[\\(R\\), \\(44\\)]\\) for either \
\[CapitalBeta] or \[GothicCapitalD], but all these attempts failed to \
generate useful equations.\"\>"], "Print",
