Cell[BoxData["\<\"We solve Case d again, but with the extra condition that \
A(t,r)=\\!\\(\\*SuperscriptBox[\\(c\\), \\(2\\)]\\). Even though a solution \
to this case can be achieved by plugging \
A(t,r)=\\!\\(\\*SuperscriptBox[\\(c\\), \\(2\\)]\\) and the formula for a(t), \
above, into the Case d \
\\!\\(\\*StyleBox[\\\"solution\\\",FontSlant->\\\"Italic\\\"]\\), it is \
possible that a different solution can be obtained by assuming \
A(t,r)=\\!\\(\\*SuperscriptBox[\\(c\\), \\(2\\)]\\) before the ODEs are \
solved, rather than after.\"\>"], "Print",
